{"version":1,"entries":{"person_138532_translations":{"at":1774731919697,"data":{"id":138532,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Lee Si-young (born Lee Eun-rae on April 17, 1982) is a South Korean actress and amateur boxer. Born Lee Eun-rae in Cheongwon County, North Chungcheong Province, her family moved to Seoul when she was nine years old. Lee majored in Fashion Design at Dongduk Women's University, and later changed her name to Lee Si-young.","name":"Lee Si-young","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이시영","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李施吟，韩国新星影视演员，毕业于同德女子大学校服装设计专业，因出演韩版《花样男子》而成名。曾在韩国第七届新人业余拳击锦标赛上夺冠，看过她比赛视频的网友大赞其“凭借拳击成了最受喜爱的艺人”。这已是李施吟在拳击比赛中的第三个冠军头衔，韩媒甚至给她起了一个“金刚芭比”的绰号，赛后她喜极而泣。","name":"李施吟","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"李施昤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"李施昤，韓國新星影視演員，畢業於同德女子大學校服裝設計專業，因出演韓版《花樣男子》而成名。曾在韓國第七屆新人業餘拳擊錦標賽上奪冠，看過她比賽視頻的網友大讚其“憑藉拳擊成了最受喜愛的藝人”。這已是李施昤在拳擊比賽中的第三個冠軍頭銜，韓媒甚至給她起了一個“金剛芭比”的綽號，賽後她喜極而泣。","name":"李施昤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"SK","iso_639_1":"sk","name":"Slovenčina","english_name":"Slovak","data":{"biography":"","name":"Lee Si-young","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ли Си Ён","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biogra